title: Setting and Surpassing Your Goals, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO38
description: Already failing your New Year's goals? Don't sweat it. Take the sheet of paper with your old goals, wipe your a** with it, and flush it down the toilet. The MFCEO is going to help you set bigger, better goals. The kind that people laugh at.
